{"tid":1585574,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際線］去旅行都可以做文宣！！！外語五大訴求整合！","createTime":"2019-09-21T16:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T13:12:25.000Z","uid":192242,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8983325bc3e1d18bfe011e8e26243f5b7c6154","tid":1585574,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"打國際戰線淨係Twitter 係唔夠架！！！<br />\n<br />\n去旅行時做文宣就可以將香港更加溶入當地！！！<br />\n<br />\n日本係香港人既鄉下，又點可以唔去做文宣呢？<br />\n<br />\n之前有手足係日本寫繪馬，但最後都比班宇宙垃圾下毒下，畫花 不特止仲要埋落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然有日本人好心幫手攞返出黎，但繪馬寫中文佢地當地人未必清楚明白我地寫緊嘜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以！！！我請左一個手足幫手翻譯五大訴求同fight for freedom, stand with Hong Kong 既日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家去到日本想寫繪馬可以直接寫日文！直接向當地人宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣一黎當地人會更加清楚香港人既訴求，更加留意香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同時可以減少一班宇宙垃圾將大家既繪馬畫花<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然仲有好多垃圾都識日文，但起碼少左一班唔識日文既垃圾下毒手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訊求  、缺一不可<br />\n五つの要求 、一つも譲らない<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（讀音版）いつつのようきゅう、ひとつもゆずらない</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港を取り戻せ、時代の革命だ<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（讀音版）ホンコンをとりもどせ、じだいのかくめいだ</span><br />\n<br />\nFight for freedom, stand with HongKong <br />\n自由のため、香港と共に<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> （讀音版）じゆうのため、ホンコンとともに</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第三行係讀音，怕玻璃心睇得明都可以寫讀音，日本人睇到應該重開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n韓文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJCJiea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJCJiea.jpg&h=15bf0120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">立即徹回暴動</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/715rf1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F715rf1b.jpg&h=1cf3c340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">徹回惡法</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4mxV1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4mxV1r.jpg&h=147a1a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行政長官下台</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GasUpU0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGasUpU0.jpg&h=b3d31a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">調查警方暴力行為</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPn5wAf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPn5wAf.jpg&h=85b05909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">立即無罪釋放所有被捕市民</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">홍콩에 민주와 자유를 지지해주셔서 감사합니다<br />\n感謝你們支持香港的民主和自由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n想係到多謝有幫手翻譯既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家記得要share比身邊既人，叫佢地去旅行既時候都幫手做下文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將香港帶去國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你有其他外語版本好歡迎你放係呢個po到，比大家多一樣參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9766083661c265d3d80e15b44418bafcc1725f2b","tid":1585574,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"d659e7988ba3c62857a053939a7c0e152e6414b1","tid":1585574,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a941dfbf67fb5761393e2e30d2743e97634f3dce","tid":1585574,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c92ade7001f552c76b0ad21d871d5fa706583365","tid":1585574,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2647dacc8d346ced2019507c294255a00ae6b4db","tid":1585574,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb43409e1e9c046daec240146895a5732450cc45","tid":1585574,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"177d9567f67b0e986e2a6fb3c38c7da43b02dfa4","tid":1585574,"uid":28485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db1982638103da19f2112f00273adc879f66580","tid":1585574,"uid":44550,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"有冇西文光復香港時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle translate信唔過"},{"pid":"8d2b200e67e241c8f4375d8917f735a69a7c4592","tid":1585574,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2db1982638103da19f2112f00273adc879f6658